                    "text": "I cannot confirm that system icons do not resize - see the attaches screenshots, one at 96 DPI running seamonkey 2.6, the other at 200 DPI running seamonkey 2.0.14 - this is how it should look, note icons on the system task panel (KDE 4.7.3). ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I myself have no strong opinion about the interface icons - trying to avoid them as much as possible, but they look ok to me zoomed.\n", 
